{"tid":831251,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[留在彼此的身邊] 你有過來自online game嘅網戀嗎?","createTime":"2018-09-21T18:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T04:59:27.000Z","uid":209193,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"51acc062b27863f602fbbd199426a6c73ab2d846","tid":831251,"uid":209193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T18:51:01.000Z","msg":"最近開左電腦d舊file睇<br />\n睇睇下就㩒左入去跑online個相薄<br />\n愈睇就愈懷念以前玩到日夜癲倒嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同時又記翻起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一個好深刻既網戀<br />\n雖然大家未見過大家 但個陣時成段關係真係好純樸 唔知係咪因為你大我幾年 每次同你分享自己嘅事 壓力都會好自然比你帶走哂 日後亦都冇再試過有咁既感覺<br />\n<br />\n我仲記得失去聯繫係因為你暑假先翻香港 <br />\n放完假你就出翻國讀書 初時仲約定下年見 <br />\n但之後我冇左件事 到我再上翻<br />\n淨低就得翻你係約定時間send嚟嘅game訊息<br />\n我仲有keep住段野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然事隔幾年 <br />\n今時今日大家都大個左唔少<br />\n記億中你都25 26歲<br />\n但我真係好想搵翻你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呻完<br />\n巴絲們都擺低一段屬於你嘅網戀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d7f58e63637836aaa52cff273471f5f442c6917","tid":831251,"uid":146340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T18:53:22.000Z","msg":"人地而家鍾意返女人啦 算吧啦"},{"pid":"0b7c084a5d38271aa2a5d4867ea9444ef7ebe15a","tid":831251,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T18:53:44.000Z","msg":"網戀係有成功例子 但主角唔係我"},{"pid":"fbc3f9cf492e0499851fc9c9a7d50140f86e2fe6","tid":831251,"uid":209193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d7f58e63637836aaa52cff273471f5f442c6917","tid":831251,"uid":146340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T18:53:22.000Z","msg":"人地而家鍾意返女人啦 算吧啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyT